member.name: STORAGE_PROTOCOL_NVME_DATA_TYPE
member.summary: Describes the type of NVMe protocol-specific data that's to be queried during an IOCTL_STORAGE_QUERY_PROPERTY request.

member.name: STORAGE_PROTOCOL_NVME_DATA_TYPE.NVMeDataTypeIdentify
member.summary: Identify data type. This can be either Identify Controller data or Identify Namespace data. When this type of data is being queried, the ProtocolDataRequestValue field of will have a value of NVME_IDENTIFY_CNS_CONTROLLER for adapter or NVME_IDENTIFY_CNS_SPECIFIC_NAMESPACE for namespace. If the ProtocolDataRequestValue is NVME_IDENTIFY_CNS_SPECIFIC_NAMESPACE, the ProtocolDataRequestSubValue field from the STORAGE_PROTOCOL_SPECIFIC_DATA structure will have a value of the namespace ID.
